                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "heightened",
                "level": 6,
                "text": "You can Cast the Spell on a willing target to suppress all memory of a particular topic, detailed in 50 words or fewer. The effect is permanent, and it patches these omissions with an indistinct haze."
