            "save_type": "Will",
            "critical_success": "The target is unaffected and realizes you tried to alter its memory.",
            "success": "The target is unaffected but thinks your spell was something harmless instead of *rewrite memory*, unless it identifies the spell.",
            "failure": "During the first 5 minutes of the spell's duration, you can Sustain the spell to modify a memory once each round. When you do, you imagine up to 6 seconds of memory to modify, to a maximum of 5 continuous minutes of memory.  \n  \n Any memories you've altered remain changed as long as the spell is active. If the target moves out of range before the 5 minutes is up, you can't alter any further memories."
